editorialNotes.standard: Express your artistic side without filling the spare room with easels and art supplies. Art Set 4 turns your iPad into a digital canvas where you can use felt markers, oil paints, watercolors, and more. editorialNotes.standard: Prêt-à-Template helps fashion designers quickly transform a look from concept to runway. The app provides figure templates with front, side, and rear views, along with the basic outline for various items of clothing that you can sketch over. The app is optimized for Apple Pencil, sensing how much pressure you apply with each stroke so you can give your designs just the right texture and intensity of color.
editorialNotes.short: Collaborate on cool ideas via SharePlay with your design team.

editorialNotes.standard: Vector art is remarkably useful—you can create completely scalable works simply by manipulating a variety of shapes. Assembly shines with accessible and intuitive features that let designers of all skill levels quickly add gorgeous objects to their photos or make artwork from the ground up. Thanks to a refined interface, you can alter your drawings easily on both iPad and iPhone. Plus, with a suite of smart sharing tools, it’s easy to collaborate with other designers.
